data.description: Enjoy the convenience of easy access to Interstate 83 and 695, which makes commuting downtown a breeze. This home is located in Mays Chapel, a community known for its friendly atmosphere, well-maintained surroundings, and communal living. 96 Blondell is a charming residence that offers a warm and inviting atmosphere with 4 bedrooms and 3.5 baths, all with a fresh touch to make it move-in ready. Come and see the spacious living areas, perfect for entertaining guests or relaxing with family. You'll love the granite kitchen countertops and the center island that provides additional eating and counter space. The fridge is equipped with a water and ice dispenser, and the deep country-style sink features a hands-free faucet. The lower level is a must-see, and the upper level is carpeted offering a master bedroom with an adjacent bathroom. Come and see it for yourself, but don't wait; this home will go fast!
